<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>

    <base href="images/">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Passenger Tasks</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }
        header {
            color: #fff;
            padding: 0px 0;
        }
        .bg {
            background-image: url("PassengerTask.jpg");
            min-height: 740px;
            background-position: center;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-size: cover;
            position: relative;
            width: 100vw;
            height: 100vh;
            animation: changeBackground 5s infinite;
        }
        .container {
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 6px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .container1 {
            background-color: #182346;
            display: flex;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0px 563px 0px 0px;
        }
        .logo img {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        .logo h1 {
            margin: 0;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background: linear-gradient(141deg, #9c26d7, #1eb1db);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            font-size: 31px;
            font-family: 'Lucida Sans', 'Lucida Sans Regular', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            font-weight: 800;
        }
        .passenger-tasks {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .tasks button,
        .tasks select {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        * {
            font-family: Open Sans;
        }
        .footer-distributed {
            background: #666;
            box-shadow: 0 1px 1px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
            box-sizing: border-box;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: left;
            font: bold 16px sans-serif;
            padding: 55px 50px;
        }
        .footer-distributed .footer-left,
        .footer-distributed .footer-center,
        .footer-distributed .footer-right {
            display: inline-block;
            vertical-align: top;
        }
        .footer-distributed .footer-left {
            width: 40%;
        }
        .footer-distributed h3 {
            color: #ffffff;
            font: normal 36px 'Open Sans', cursive;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .footer-distributed h3 span {
            color: lightseagreen;
        }
        .footer-distributed .footer-links {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 20px 0 12px;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .footer-distributed .footer-links a {
            display: inline-block;
            line-height: 1.8;
            font-weight: 400;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
        }
        .footer-distributed .footer-company-name {
            color: #222;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: normal;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .footer-distributed .footer-center {
            width: 35%;
        }
        .footer-distributed .footer-center i {
            background-color: #33383b;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 25px;
            width: 38px;
            height: 38px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 42px;
            margin: 10px 15px;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }
        .footer-distributed .footer-center i.fa-envelope {
            font-size: 17px;
            line-height: 38px;
        }
        .footer-distributed .footer-center p {
            display: inline-block;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-weight: 400;
            vertical-align: middle;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .footer-distributed .footer-center p span {
            display: block;
            font-weight: normal;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 2;
        }
        .footer-distributed .footer-center p a {
            color: lightseagreen;
            text-decoration: none;;
        }
        .footer-distributed .footer-links a:before {
            content: "|";
            font-weight: 300;
            font-size: 20px;
            left: 0;
            color: #fff;
            display: inline-block;
            padding-right: 5px;
        }
        .footer-distributed .footer-links .link-1:before {
            content: none;
        }
        .footer-distributed .footer-right {
            width: 20%;
        }
        .footer-distributed .footer-company-about {
            line-height: 20px;
            color: #92999f;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: normal;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .footer-distributed .footer-company-about span {
            display: block;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .footer-distributed .footer-icons {
            margin-top: 25px;
        }
        .footer-distributed .footer-icons a {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 35px;
            height: 35px;
            cursor: pointer;
            background-color: #33383b;
            border-radius: 2px;
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 35px;
            margin-right: 3px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 880px) {
            .footer-distributed {
                font: bold 14px sans-serif;
            }
            .footer-distributed .footer-left,
            .footer-distributed .footer-center,
            .footer-distributed .footer-right {
                display: block;
                width: 100%;
                margin-bottom: 40px;
                text-align: center;
            }
            .footer-distributed .footer-center i {
                margin-left: 0;
            }
        }
        .btn {
            background-color: #131c39;
            margin: 5px;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: white;
            color: #182346;
        }
        .passenger-tasks h2 {
            font-family: cursive;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: x-large;
        }
        .faq {
            padding: 40px;
        }
        .container {
            margin: auto;
        }
        .containerbdy {
            margin: 7.125rem auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .containerbdy h2 {
            text-align: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 25px;
            font-family: cursive;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .card {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
        }
        .card-img-top {
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }
        .faq {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .faq-question {
            position: relative;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #182346;
        }

        .toggle-button {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #666;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .faq-answer {
            display: none;
            color: #333;
        }

        .toggle-button:hover {
            color: #182346;
        }
        .text-center{
          font-family: cursive;
          color: #131c39;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
    <div class="bg">
        <div class="container container1">
            <div class="logo navbar-left">
                <img src="railwaysystemlogo.png" alt="Railway Logo">
                <h1>RailEase</h1>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="passenger-tasks">
        <h1>Welcome, < %= passengerName %>!</h1>
        
        <div class="tasks">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    <button href="Booking.html" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block">Apply for Booking</button>
                </div >
                   <select class="form-control mb-4">
                  <option>Economy</option>
                  <option>Business</option>
                  <option>First Class</option>
              </select>
          </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-6">
              <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block">Station List</button>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
              <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block">Train List</button>
          </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-6">
              <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block">Route List</button>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
              <a href="index.html" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block">Logout</a>
          </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-12">
              <button class="btn btn-info btn-lg btn-block">Check Booking Status</button>
          </div>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>
</header>

<div class="container containerbdy mt-4">
<h2>Why book from RailEase</h2>
<div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
  <div class="card">
      <img class="card-img-top" src="Track.webp" alt="Card image">
      <div class="card-body">
          <h4 class="card-title">Live Train Tracking</h4>
          <p class="card-text">Track the real-time location of your train and stay updated on delays or changes.</p>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
  <div class="card">
      <img class="card-img-top" src="Wifi.webp" alt="Card image">
      <div class="card-body">
          <h4 class="card-title">Free WiFi</h4>
          <p class="card-text">Enjoy free high-speed internet connectivity across all major railway stations.</p>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
  <div class="card">
      <img class="card-img-top" src="SSL security.jpg" alt="Card image">
      <div class="card-body">
          <h4 class="card-title">SSL Security</h4>
          <p class="card-text">Our payment system is secured with SSL encryption to protect your sensitive information.</p>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
  <div class="card">
      <img class="card-img-top" src="Payment.jpg" alt="Card image">
      <div class="card-body">
          <h4 class="card-title">Mobile Payments</h4>
          <p class="card-text">Convenient mobile payment options for users on the go.</p>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="container mt-5">
  <h2 class="text-center">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ) - RailEase eBooking</h2>
  <div class="faq">
      <h4 class="faq-question">What is RailEase eBooking?<span class="toggle-button">+</span></h4>
      <p class="faq-answer" style="display: none;">RailEase eBooking is an online platform that allows you to book train tickets, check train schedules, and manage your bookings conveniently from your computer or mobile device.</p>
       <hr>
      <h4 class="faq-question">How do I create an account on RailEase?<span class="toggle-button">+</span></h4>
      <p class="faq-answer" style="display: none;">To create an account, click on the "Sign Up" button on the RailEase homepage. Fill in your personal details, choose a username and password, and submit the form. You will receive a confirmation email to verify your account.</p>
     <hr>
      <h4 class="faq-question">How can I check my booking status?<span class="toggle-button">+</span></h4>
      <p class="faq-answer" style="display: none;">To check your booking status, log in to your RailEase account and navigate to the "My Bookings" section. Here, you can view the status of all your bookings.</p>
     <hr>
      <h4 class="faq-question">How do I book a train ticket?<span class="toggle-button">+</span></h4>
      <p class="faq-answer" style="display: none;">To book a train ticket, log in to your RailEase account, select your route and travel dates, choose your preferred train and class, and proceed to payment. You will receive a confirmation email with your booking details.</p>
      <hr>
      <h4 class="faq-question">Can I cancel or change my booking?<span class="toggle-button">+</span></h4>
      <p class="faq-answer" style="display: none;">Yes, you can cancel or change your booking by logging into your account and accessing the "My Bookings" section. Please note that cancellation and change fees may apply, depending on the fare rules.</p>
      <hr>
      <h4 class="faq-question">How will I receive my ticket?<span class="toggle-button">+</span></h4>
      <p class="faq-answer" style="display: none;">Once your booking is confirmed, you will receive an e-ticket via email. You can also download and print your ticket from the "My Bookings" section of your RailEase account.</p>
       <hr>
       <h4 class="faq-question"> What payment methods are accepted?<span class="toggle-button">+</span>
        <p class="faq-answer" style="display: none;"> RailEase accepts various payment methods, including credit/debit cards, net banking, and digital wallets. Select your preferred payment method at checkout.</p>
        <hr>
        <h4 class="faq-question">Is my payment information secure?<span class="toggle-button">+</span>
        <p class="faq-answer" style="display: none;"> Yes, RailEase uses advanced encryption technology to ensure that your payment information is secure and confidential.</p>
        <hr>
        <h4 class="faq-question">How do I get a refund for a cancelled booking?<span class="toggle-button">+</span>
        <p class="faq-answer" style="display: none;"> Refunds for cancelled bookings are processed according to our cancellation policy. Once your cancellation request is approved, the refund amount will be credited to your original payment method within a few business days.</h4>
        </p>
         
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Footer -->
<footer class="footer-distributed" style="background-color: #131c39;">    
<div class="footer-left">
<h3>RailEase<span></span></h3>
<p class="footer-links">
  <a href="#" class="link-1">Home</a>
  
  <a href="#">Blog</a>

  <a href="#">Pricing</a>

  <a href="#">About</a>
  
  <a href="#">Faq</a>
  
  <a href="#">Contact</a>
</p>

<p class="footer-company-name">RailEase © 2015</p>
</div>

<div class="footer-center">
<div>
  <i class="fa fa-map-marker"></i>
  <p><span>106 A. Mughalpura Station</span> Mughalpura Station, Lahore</p>
</div>

<div>
  <i class="fa fa-phone"></i>
  <p>+92-345-958-2324</p>
</div>

<div>
  <i class="fa fa-envelope"></i>
  <p><a href="mailto:support@company.com">support@railease.com</a></p>
</div>

</div>

<div class="footer-right">

<p class="footer-company-about">
  <span>RailEase</span>
  The RailEase project aims to modernize and enhance the country's railway infrastructure, catering to the growing demands of passengers and freight transportation. With a focus on efficiency, safety, and comfort, the project encompasses various initiatives, including the renovation of existing stations and the construction of new ones equipped with state-of-the-art facilities.
</p>

<div class="footer-icons">
  <a href="#"><i class="fa fa-facebook"></i></a>
  <a href="#"><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i></a>
  <a href="#"><i class="fa fa-linkedin"></i></a>
  <a href="#"><i class="fa fa-github"></i></a>

</div>
</div>
</footer>

<!-- Bootstrap and jQuery -->
<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>


<script>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
        const toggleButtons = document.querySelectorAll('.toggle-button');

        toggleButtons.forEach(function(button) {
            button.addEventListener('click', function() {
                const answer = this.parentElement.nextElementSibling;
                if (answer.style.display === 'none') {
                    answer.style.display = 'block';
                    this.textContent = '-';
                } else {
                    answer.style.display = 'none';
                    this.textContent = '+';
                }
            });
        });
    });
</script>
<script>
    $(document).ready(function() {
        // Placeholder for dynamic welcome message
        $("#welcome-placeholder").text(welcomeMessage);
    });
</script>

</body>
</html>

